/*
 * Nixon Diamond -- classic inheritance example.
 * Kept as a later semantic-CR test case.
 */

<Extremist>: Nixon is an extremist.
  + <Hawk>: Nixon is a hawk.
    + <Republican>: Nixon is a Republican.
    - <Quaker>: Nixon is a Quaker.
  + <Pacifist>: Nixon is a pacifist.
    + <Quaker>
    - <Republican>
